_______________________________________________________________________________
"Recall"          
        If a psionicist purchases this ability and uses it while dead
        they may draw upon the "Psionic Convergence of Minds" to
        merge them back into a physical body, so that they may
        continue their adventure from the point at which they
        died.
        It costs nothing to use.
 
SP Cost:  none		Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  recall
